#MEM id=error-tracking source=/root/yvon/agent-department/shared/skills/custom/error-tracking/SKILL.md
M|error-tracking|name: error-tracking-shared
M|error-tracking|description: Shared error tracking standard for all YVON agents. Defines structured log format, error classification, HTTP status rules, and no-PII policy. Source of truth referenced by Raj, Dev, Mia,
M|error-tracking|version: 1.1.0
M|error-tracking|applies-to: all-tec-agents
M|error-tracking|> Canonical source: `shared/skills/custom/error-tracking/SKILL.md`
M|error-tracking|> Raj's copy at `tec/raj/skills/custom/error-tracking/SKILL.md` is the origin — this shared file mirrors it.
M|error-tracking|> If they conflict, update Raj's file and sync here.
M|error-tracking|Every route error MUST follow this shape before logging:
M|error-tracking|```typescript
M|error-tracking|interface YVONErrorLog {
M|error-tracking|type: 'route_error' | 'auth_error' | 'db_error' | 'external_api_error' | 'validation_error'
M|error-tracking|route: string          // '/api/[exact-route-name]'
M|error-tracking|method: 'GET' | 'POST' | 'PUT' | 'DELETE' | 'PATCH'
M|error-tracking|message: string        // user-safe message only — NOT err.message
M|error-tracking|venture_slug: string   // ctx for multi-vtr debugging, not PII
M|error-tracking|timestamp: string      // new Date().toISOString()
M|error-tracking|// NEVER include: stack trace, err.message, API keys, email, name, payment info
M|error-tracking|}
M|error-tracking|```
M|error-tracking|**Implementation (copy into any route file that needs error logging):**
M|error-tracking|```typescript
M|error-tracking|function logError(error: Partial<YVONErrorLog>) {
M|error-tracking|console.error(JSON.stringify({
M|error-tracking|type: error.type ?? 'route_error',
M|error-tracking|route: error.route,
M|error-tracking|method: error.method,
M|error-tracking|message: error.message ?? 'An error occurred.',
M|error-tracking|venture_slug: error.venture_slug ?? 'unknown',
M|error-tracking|timestamp: new Date().toISOString()
M|error-tracking|}))
M|error-tracking|}
M|error-tracking|```
M|error-tracking|| Error type | When to use | Log level |
M|error-tracking||-----------|------------|-----------|
M|error-tracking|| `validation_error` | Zod parse failed, bad input | `console.warn` |
M|error-tracking|| `auth_error` | getUser() failed, ses expired | `console.warn` |
M|error-tracking|| `route_error` | Unexpected error in handler | `console.error` |
M|error-tracking|| `db_error` | Supabase query failed | `console.error` |
M|error-tracking|| `external_api_error` | Apify, YouTube, GA4 failure | `console.warn` |
M|error-tracking|`4xx` errors → WARN (client fault) · `5xx` errors → ERROR (our system fault)
M|error-tracking|| Scenario | Status |
M|error-tracking||----------|--------|
M|error-tracking|| Zod validation failed | `400` |
M|error-tracking|| Missing or invalid auth | `401` |
M|error-tracking|| Authenticated, not authorized | `403` |
M|error-tracking|| Resource not found | `404` |
M|error-tracking|| Rate limit exceeded | `429` + `Retry-After` header |
M|error-tracking|| Unexpected server error | `500` |
M|error-tracking|| Dependency unavailable | `503` + `Retry-After: 5` |
M|error-tracking|**Non-negotiable:** Never return `200` with an error body. Never `500` for client input. Never `401` for authorization failure (that is `403`).
M|error-tracking|**Never log:** email, full names, phone, payment data, ses/auth tokens, raw API keys, IP addresses.
M|error-tracking|**Safe to log:** `user_id` (UUID only), `venture_slug`, `route`, `method`, HTTP status code, generic user-safe message.
M|error-tracking|```typescript
M|error-tracking|export async function POST(req: NextRequest) {
M|error-tracking|const ventureSlug = req.headers.get('x-vtr-slug') ?? 'unknown'
M|error-tracking|try {
M|error-tracking|// handler logic
M|error-tracking|} catch (err) {
M|error-tracking|logError({ type: 'route_error', route: '/api/[route]', method: 'POST', message: 'An unexpected error occurred.', venture_slug: ventureSlug })
M|error-tracking|return NextResponse.json({ error: 'An unexpected error occurred. Please try again.' }, { status: 500 })
M|error-tracking|}
M|error-tracking|}
M|error-tracking|```
M|error-tracking|| agt | Role |
